move1.name: Psybeam
move1.description: The target is attacked with a peculiar ray. It may also confuse the target.

move2.name: Confusion
move2.description: The target is struck by a peculiar ray. This may also leave the target confused.

move3.name: Shadow Ball
move3.description: The user hurls a shadowy blob at the target. It may also lower the target's Special Defense stat.

move4.name: Psychic
move4.description: The target is hit by a strong telekinetic force. It may also reduce the target's Special Defense stat.
